      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Dec 31, 2006 picture caption with article about film based on The Kite Runner (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture caption last Sunday with an article about a film based on Khaled Hosseini's novel ''The Kite Runner'' reversed the identifications for two men involved in the production, based on information provided by the studio. The novelist was on the left, and the director, Marc Forster, was on the right.</p>
      </block>
